<HEADLINE> New Industrial Area planned in Uganda </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KAMPALA, December 13 (Xinhua) -- Uganda is planning a new
industrial area in the central Uganda and has finished
preliminary survey for it, local media reported today.
</P>
<P>
