<TEXT>
<P>
BEIRUT, December 13 (Xinhua) -- Lebanese Minister of Economy
and Trade Yassin Jaber has announced that Lebanon has won its bid
to host the prestigious seventh Islamic Trade Fair (ITF) of the
Organization of Islamic Conference (OIC).
</P>
<P>
"Lebanese International Fairs and Promotions (IFP) on Thursday
was appointed to be the official organizer of the event," today's
local newspaper the Daily Star quoted Jaber saying.
</P>
<P>
