Than Shwe will also attend an informal summit meeting of ASEAN
leaders and their counterparts from China, Japan and South Korea.
</P>
<P>
Myanmar has been working closely with ASEAN, forming respective
committees and groups in all sectors and taking part in various
meetings and activities of the regional grouping since its
admission.  
