<HEADLINE> Americans Dominate Freestyle Skiing Aerials </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, December 12 (Xinhua) -- Americans clinched both man's
and women's titles in World Cup freestyle skiing as former world
champion Nikki Stone winning her second meet of the season and
Britt Swartley taking the men's event in Tignes, France on
Friday, .
</P>
